[b]Uses varargs, which represents an infinite amount of parameters.[/b]

Eg:

[code=java]questLayout("Kingdom Wars", 
"I should talk to the old man by the portal", 
"I must have these skills:", 
"70 Thieving/85 Fletching/15 Mining/", 
"50 Smithing");[/code]

or

[code=java]questLayout("Kingdom Wars", 
"@str@I should talk to the old man by the portal", 
"@str@I must have these skills:",
"@str@70 Thieving/85 Fletching/15 Mining/",
"@str@50 Smithing",
"I should speak to the duke in lumbridge castle");
[/code]


